data.description:
Welcome home! This lovely townhome on an oak-lined street in Avalon Park
has been meticulously maintained, tastefully updated, and is ready for new
owners. This end unit townhome has 3 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, a den, 2 car
garage, and a fenced in courtyard. The A/C was replaced in 2021, new roof October 2023, new garage door opener 2023, W/D is two years old, recessed lighting was added 2023, kitchen has a newer water filtration system, and all fans/light fixtures/faucets/hardware have been updated. All appliances stay!

HOA covers cable TV, community pools, maintenance of the exterior, and maintenance of the grounds. The community has 2 pools, tennis courts, walking/bike trails, parks, a community center and more.

You are a short walk away from the restaurants, shops and parks of downtown Avalon Park. The community has many events throughout the year. Come check this one out before its gone!
